          "reviewBody": "Worst school ever... There is no proper response for parents. Even they did not inform whether the kids have school or not. Most of the staffs are not allow the kids for nature calls too. Only Money minded school. They are not conducting parents meeting not even a single time in a year. They r not allow parents to bring lunch for kids. Staffs r very rude and kindless peoples",
